    "centralSearchIntent": "Informational,Non-branded,Non-local",
    "sourceContextBridge": "GetForked matches businesses with approved builders for custom AI automation systems.",
    "contextualVector": "H1: AI Automation Agency\nH2: When ai automation agency needs more than a generic tool\nH3: Common failure modes\nH3: What buyers usually need\nH2: What a custom AI automation build can replace\nH3: Workflow example\nH2: How GetForked matches the right builder\nH2: Cost and scoping context\nH2: Related AI automation pages",
